data.title: Welcome to O'Brien Funeral Home! [Wall & Brick, New Jersey]
data.meta_description: Our inclusive family-owned funeral home has offered high-quality burials, cremations, ash scattering, and veterans services at affordable prices since 1966.
data.text:
Welcome to O'Brien Funeral Home

-Wall & Brick, NJ-

For over 50 years, O'Brien Funeral Home has been taking care of families in Wall Township, Brick and the surrounding communities of Spring Lake, Belmar, Avon, Manasquan, Brielle, Neptune, Neptune City, Ocean, Point Pleasant, and Howell. During their most difficult times of need, it is a responsibility that we take with great pride and even greater humility.

Our Affordable Funeral Homes in New Jersey

Explore our website, or stop into one of our funeral homes to see why we are a leading funeral home in New Jersey. We are proud of our compassionate, professional staff and exceptional funeral, burial & cremation services.

Contact us and let us help you start the planning process.
